'''克里斯·斯圖爾特'''（Chris Stewart；{{bd|1960年|7月15日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位作家、商人、政治人物。自2013年開始，他是[[猶他州|猶他州]]第2選舉區選出的美國眾議院議員。他的黨籍是[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]。他曾在美國空軍服役，創下世界最快不經停繞行世界一周的飛行記錄<ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/03/books/review/InsideList-t.html| title = Inside the List| year = 2011| publisher = The New York Times| accessdate = November 11, 2011| archive-date = 2018-12-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181206111609/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/03/books/review/InsideList-t.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>。退役之後，斯圖爾特成為一名商人和暢銷書作家<ref>{{cite web| first = Chris| last = Stewart| url = http://www.shadowmountain.com/products-page/nonfiction/seven-miracles-that-saved-america/| title = Seven Miracles That Saved America| publisher = Shadow Mountain| year = 2009| accessdate = November 11, 2011| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://archive.is/20120911102737/http://www.shadowmountain.com/products-page/nonfiction/seven-miracles-that-saved-america/| archivedate = 2012年9月11日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| first = Chris| last = Stewart| url = http://www.shadowmountain.com/products-page/new-releases/the-miracle-of-freedom-7-tipping-points-that-saved-the-world/| title = The Miracle of Freedom: Seven Tipping Points That Saved the World| year = 2011| publisher = Shadow Mountain| accessdate = November 11, 2011| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111110061954/http://www.shadowmountain.com/products-page/new-releases/the-miracle-of-freedom-7-tipping-points-that-saved-the-world/| archivedate = 2011年11月10日}}</ref>。
